find where it is 

You can test that you have the right path with:
drush php-eval "fopen('./working/directory/path/hub_pages.txt', r);"

If this command throws no errors, you can use that path/filename in the cache-warmer command.

cd
~/.drush
git clone --branch 7.x-4.x http://git.drupal.org/project/cache_warmer.git
cd cache_warmer
drush cache-warmer --updated-last='-2 days' --hub-pages-file=hub_pages.txt https://webital.co.uk
drush cache-warmer --updated-last='-2 days' --hub-pages-file=hub_pages.txt http://shopwiz.net
Create your hub pages file.
